*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&  Include  ZBC_INCL_RUNTIME
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*

*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&      Form  FRM_GET_REP_DATA
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*       获取报表运行数据
*----------------------------------------------------------------------*
*      -->I_REPID    报表名称
*      -->IT_SELTAB  选择参数表
*      -->ER_DATA    返回结果
*----------------------------------------------------------------------*
FORM FRM_GET_REP_DATA  USING I_REPID   TYPE CLIKE
                             IT_SELTAB TYPE ZBCTT_RSPARAML
                             ER_DATA   TYPE REF TO DATA.

* 参数设置
  CALL METHOD CL_SALV_BS_RUNTIME_INFO=>SET
    EXPORTING
      DISPLAY  = ABAP_FALSE
      METADATA = ABAP_FALSE
      DATA     = ABAP_TRUE.

* Submit
  SUBMIT (I_REPID) WITH SELECTION-TABLE IT_SELTAB AND RETURN.

  TRY.
      CALL METHOD CL_SALV_BS_RUNTIME_INFO=>GET_DATA_REF
        IMPORTING
          R_DATA = ER_DATA.
    CATCH CX_SALV_BS_SC_RUNTIME_INFO .
      MESSAGE 'Unable to retrieve ALV data! Please try other conditions.' TYPE 'E'.
  ENDTRY.

  CALL METHOD CL_SALV_BS_RUNTIME_INFO=>CLEAR_ALL.
ENDFORM.                    " FRM_GET_REP_DATA
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&      Form  FRM_GET_REP_RESULT
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*       获取报表运行结果(部分字段)
*----------------------------------------------------------------------*
*      -->T_RESULT    运行结果
*      -->I_REPID     报表名称
*      -->IT_SELTAB   选择参数表
*----------------------------------------------------------------------*
FORM FRM_GET_REP_RESULT  TABLES T_RESULT
                          USING I_REPID   TYPE CLIKE
                                IT_SELTAB TYPE ZBCTT_RSPARAML.
  DATA: LR_DATA TYPE REF TO DATA.
  FIELD-SYMBOLS: <LT_DATA> TYPE ANY TABLE.
  FIELD-SYMBOLS: <LS_DATA>.

* 获取报表运行数据
  PERFORM FRM_GET_REP_DATA USING I_REPID IT_SELTAB LR_DATA.
  ASSIGN LR_DATA->* TO <LT_DATA>.
  CHECK SY-SUBRC EQ 0.

* 返回指定字段
  LOOP AT <LT_DATA> ASSIGNING <LS_DATA>.
    MOVE-CORRESPONDING <LS_DATA> TO T_RESULT.
    APPEND T_RESULT.
    CLEAR T_RESULT.
  ENDLOOP.
ENDFORM.                    " FRM_GET_REP_RESULT
